item.title: CalCentral alerts and release notes are unavailable
item.description: As of this morning, Friday, August 7, 2015, the CalCentral web application lost access to system-wide alerts and information on the latest release. We expect the problem to be resolved with the next maintenance update of CalCentral, scheduled for Sunday, August 9, 2015, between 10:00am and 11:00am.
